Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你们  按我说的动动手看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是杀害赛门·汉特的机关
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是称为「活结」的绑法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳结的魔术里经常使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女摩瑞拉就是这样解开绳子  拿到短剑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.67,0:00:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这根本算不上混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正想重新拼凑的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啊嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢刚才帮了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像来的时候也是一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  有空位哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  那个我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  能一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了啊  其他地方全都是满员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…两位是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有座位在迷惘的时候  这位先生就在走廊上叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  来自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样坐一起也是一种缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  你为什么会去那种修道院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道自己的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那样死后去黄泉国的时候会迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想要找到它  就参加魔术幻灯秀之夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  阿姨你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就是稻草人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常在偏远乡下的农场里  监视着坏小鸟们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  这是什么游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思  那我就算是骑士了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑着爱马在荒野上奔驰  把坏人一个个全部砍倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:03:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樵夫就好了  我做不了那么勇猛的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多就只能砍砍树了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是胆小的少爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高贵太古灰狼和其糊涂仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  我绝对不是糊涂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx70\fscy70\pos(457,647)}Masquerade
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面舞会号这名字起得真是妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是如假面舞会一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.13,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,560)}漆黑的列车运送着几个谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信吗  幼狼能把那个盒子夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个对我们灰狼来说就是王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能从迫近的暴风雨中保护那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就托付给她了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们要怎么办  难得都跑到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:05:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心  办法其它还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿啊  解开谜团  然后为了活下去而展示力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失踪的雷格兰千金至今行踪不明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏瓦尔发生这种案件了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来刚才有什么想说的  是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城  遗物箱是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有相关的知识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗物箱就是  一部分欧洲地区流传的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的箱子里  放满了各种表现人生章节的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人死了之后箱子会和棺材一起埋葬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是人生的象征之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在别西卜的头骨里的那个箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕也封印着某人的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后妈妈她们想要得到那个箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗物箱  必须要查明它的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们  全身湿着的话会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和乘务员说  借点什么穿的来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吹夜风吹的有点冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让阿姨也帮我拿一份来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷就在这等着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现公主愿望的是  骑士的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来幽会的吗  在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢弃稻草人的职责  对别人的收获出手真是不规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我伙伴那里拿来的东西  还给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊  他们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  刚才听到了不该听的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:07:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日  能找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚  刚才外面有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  替换的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…稻草人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好遇见熟人  好像换房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去换衣服了  久城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到的确实不是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知生死  但是已经有人从这舞台上退场了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说刚才的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是自称稻草人的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个房间里面的所有人  不是灵异部就是学院的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来混进不得了的假面舞会了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经想好办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这舞蹈的中心里的应该就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要如此断言混沌的碎片还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  因为太合身了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说合身  想让我伺候你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得了不起了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我  我一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无线？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樵夫  在和谁通话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太慢  就来找你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  樵夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去餐车吗  一直喝到天亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊  不过得是你请客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能招待我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  伏特加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取葡萄干游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把火里的葡萄快速取出来吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后说出自己愿望的游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的真清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  谁先来拿这个葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  可以的话我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我先来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明年也想看到故乡的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为喜欢鸢尾那美丽的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了这个的话  要背叛同伴的樵夫们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这葡萄吃了不会中毒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝点水会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说愿望来着？  这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也希望你能平安回到故乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此话怎讲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  别喝那水！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别演戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你下的毒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在场的有医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我下毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说  你也看见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也吃了同一盆的葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水我也喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒是下在杯底  冻得薄薄的一层
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和她最初喝的时候  毒还没溶解在水中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而就当冰开始融化  她再次喝的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  你不适合手枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷格兰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  这荒唐假面舞会所围绕的中心是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的灵异部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这盒子我死也不会给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子？  那果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  太勉强了  这样乱动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了  反正这列车上的所有人都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的定时联络一旦中断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伙就会让这列车脱轨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其让灵异部夺走那个  不如毁掉整辆列车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就给我待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去控制室  让火车停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加  就在那等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧  抓紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来骑士意外落马了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子…谁也…绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的性命才更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁桥…里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕  我想知道生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这距离还是太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是引爆装置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让这列车脱轨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子弹只剩下一发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我  下次一定打中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那不可能  还是我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说过  为了活下去而展现自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要亲手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  但是我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  让你帮我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人和仆人要齐心协力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城  对于灰狼来说没有任何不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经验什么的不过是愚蠢的野蛮人的胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我没开过枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却熟悉它的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  你一定做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡过这场风暴  我们俩一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我们的圣玛格丽特学园
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  你做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  接下来该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没煤了  迟早会自己停下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失踪的雷格兰小姐的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵异部绑架了你的妹妹作为人质
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能利用你当临时间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜如此他们也想得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个遗物箱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有描述某个男人一生的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从盒子主人的身上切下来的脐带
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他的肖像画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意中人的香水瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后他遇到了挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「绝不回头」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只写了一句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面就只有这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这遗物箱还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说这盒子的主人还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这盒子不是在坟墓中而是藏在某人家的地板下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那无名村  藏着我妈妈照片的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  盒子的主人和柯蒂丽亚女士一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他之名为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘比特·罗杰  七岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在塞伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学院领导人  丘比特·罗杰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏是有浓厚风俗的无名村出身的灰狼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是足以撼动政治力量的平衡的重大事实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  灵异部…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想夺取这箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后科学院拼命也要阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重新拼凑的就这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道灵异部会怎么用它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有这个箱子的话  你妹妹就能得救了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:21:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那东西交给布洛瓦侯爵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.22,0:22:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈交给我的谜题我解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手上还有王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有馅饼  也没有杏仁饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有馅饼也有杏仁饼干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.70,0:24:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  这是歌词…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.31,0:24:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:19.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(638,550)}蔷薇色的人生被埋于新雪之下


